node.text: Got to chat with @danawhite about the fights this weekend. Gave my predictions, let’s see how much I know 😁

node.text: Just like these doors, my @amazon EU stores just opened. They’re filled with goodies I love 🥰

node.text: First top 5 of the year. Still more to come but gonna take it for now with a smile 🙂 awesome to have these full crowds back too 🥳 glad to see Max walk away from that, let’s wish him well 🙏🏼

node.text: Daren on the right.. wait. Even I’m confused now. Anyways, here is the legend that is Daren.

node.text: Hello fans. Hope everyone enjoyed qualifying. See you tomorrow 😊

node.text: Never did I think I’d drive one of my hero’s race cars. Pretty damn special 😌 thank you @mclaren @fosgoodwood

node.text: Yesterday was fun. Very happy for everyone at @mclaren. Triple header is done. Everyone can catch up on some rest now 😌 and belated thank you for the birthday wishes. I’m still 31 as covid year doesn’t count.

node.text: Today went well. Drove fast, felt good. Bit of fine tuning tonight and we’ll be good to go for qualifying tomorrow 🤠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Daniel Ricciardo on June 21, 2021 tagging @mclaren. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Great team result yesterday. Mansour was riding with us, happy we could put on a bit of a show. See y’all in 6 days 🚥
